{"meta":{"instanceId":"148ba950667ef04d0c16951c0250998ce6284ec0fd24f99df14953aba6dd4949","templateCredsSetupCompleted":true},"nodes":[{"id":"ab90c9a0-7ea8-439c-8b03-d3cd622327ac","name":"When clicking ‘Execute workflow’","type":"n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger","position":[1696,528],"parameters":{},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"09114583-2658-463b-b3fe-4ae7caa4139d","name":"Sticky Note","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[368,16],"parameters":{"width":1200,"height":1184,"content":"# Hosting Static HTML KPI Dashboard with CustomJS\n\n[KPI Google Sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10mj6hngkPTg1_A6bVNn8QfKujap6j-Lrt_LwAkY2d7Q/edit?usp=sharing)  \n\nThis workflow automatically generates a weekly KPI dashboard from Google Sheets data and hosts it as a live static HTML page using [CustomJS](https://www.customjs.space).\n\n---\n\n## Setup\n- Requires a **self-hosted n8n instance** and a **CustomJS API key**.\n- Google Sheets should be **publicly accessible** or shared with a service account for n8n access.\n- Optional: Additional JSON/CSV sources can be integrated.\n\n---\n\n## How it works\n1 **Manual Trigger**  \n- Run the workflow on demand or schedule weekly.\n\n\n2 **Load Data from Google Sheet**  \n- Pull KPI metrics such as Visitors, Leads, Demo Booked, Proposal Sent, Won.  \n- Aggregate weekly or per channel as needed.\n\n\n3 **Prepare Structured JSON**  \n- Transform sheet rows into a clean JSON structure ready for the dashboard.  \n- Example structure: \n```json\n[\n  {\"Date\":\"2026-02-01\",\"Channel\":\"Google Ads\",\"Visitors\":1200,\"Leads\":95,\"Demo Booked\":40,\"Proposal Sent\":22,\"Won\":9},\n  {\"Date\":\"2026-02-01\",\"Channel\":\"LinkedIn\",\"Visitors\":800,\"Leads\":70,\"Demo Booked\":28,\"Proposal Sent\":16,\"Won\":7}\n]\n```\n\n4 **Generate HTML Dashboard**  \n- Feed JSON into a CustomJS HTML template node.\n- Automatically builds KPI cards, tables, and charts using Chart.js.\n\n\n5 **Host Static HTML**\n- CustomJS deploys the HTML page instantly.\n- Optional: Connect a custom domain in one click.\n- Each weekly update overwrites the previous dashboard.\n\n\n6 **Optional Enhancements**\n- Generate QR codes for the live dashboard link.\n- Include multiple charts, multiple sheets, or historical trends."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"322cf06a-f67e-4673-b73f-8ab6e077240a","name":"Sticky Note1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1616,432],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":960,"height":416,"content":"## Collect sheet data and convert to json"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"ec27944e-b41a-4da7-baec-e7f0b6512939","name":"Sticky Note2","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[2688,432],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":1168,"height":432,"content":"## Build and publish HTML"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"8890abe9-d06b-4a8d-a4bb-64d1c421f235","name":"Sticky Note3","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[4000,432],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":432,"height":416,"content":"## Generate QR code"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d00fd93c-a23c-42c2-9a15-7c05ba2f9efd","name":"HTML","type":"n8n-nodes-base.html","position":[2800,576],"parameters":{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>KPI Dashboard</title>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n\n<style>\nbody{\n  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n  background:#f6f7fb;\n  margin:0;\n  padding:24px;\n  color:#111;\n}\n.container{\n  max-width:1100px;\n  margin:auto;\n}\nh1{margin-bottom:4px;}\n.subtitle{color:#666;margin-bottom:30px;}\n\n.cards{\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));\n  gap:16px;\n  margin-bottom:30px;\n}\n.card{\n  background:white;\n  padding:18px;\n  border-radius:12px;\n  box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n}\n.card .label{font-size:13px;color:#666}\n.card .value{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;margin-top:6px}\n\n.charts{\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;\n  gap:24px;\n  margin-bottom:24px;\n}\n@media(max-width:900px){\n  .charts{\n    grid-template-columns:1fr;\n  }\n}\ncanvas{\n  max-height:280px;\n}\n\n.section{\n  background:white;\n  padding:18px;\n  border-radius:12px;\n  margin-bottom:24px;\n  box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n}\n\ntable{\n  width:100%;\n  border-collapse:collapse;\n}\nth,td{\n  padding:10px;\n  border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\n  text-align:left;\n  font-size:14px;\n}\nth{color:#666;font-weight:600;}\n\n.footer{\n  text-align:center;\n  margin-top:30px;\n  color:#999;\n  font-size:12px;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<h1 id=\"title\"></h1>\n<div class=\"subtitle\" id=\"period\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"cards\" id=\"kpiCards\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"charts\">\n\n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h3>Visitors by Channel</h3>\n    <canvas id=\"visitorsChart\"></canvas>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"section\">\n    <h3>Funnel Conversion</h3>\n    <canvas id=\"funnelChart\"></canvas>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"section\">\n  <h3>Channel Breakdown</h3>\n  <table id=\"table\"></table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer\">\nGenerated automatically • KPI Dashboard\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n/* ===== JSON Daten ===== */\nconst report = {\n  reportTitle: \"Weekly Sales Funnel Report\",\n  period: \"Week ending 2026-02-01\",\n  data: {{ JSON.stringify($json.data) }}\n};\n\n/* ===== Totals berechnen ===== */\nconst totals = report.data.reduce((a,c)=>({\n  visitors: a.visitors + c[\"Visitors\"] || 0,\n  leads: a.leads + c[\"Leads\"] || 0,\n  demo: a.demo + c[\"Demo Booked\"] || 0,\n  proposal: a.proposal + c[\"Proposal Sent\"] || 0,\n  won: a.won + c[\"Won\"] || 0\n}), {visitors:0, leads:0, demo:0, proposal:0, won:0});\n\n/* ===== KPIs ===== */\nconst leadRate = ((totals.leads / totals.visitors)*100).toFixed(1);\nconst closeRate = ((totals.won / totals.leads)*100).toFixed(1);\n\n/* ===== HEADER ===== */\ndocument.getElementById(\"title\").textContent = report.reportTitle;\ndocument.getElementById(\"period\").textContent = report.period;\n\n/* ===== KPI CARDS ===== */\nconst cards = [\n  [\"Visitors\", totals.visitors],\n  [\"Leads\", totals.leads],\n  [\"Deals Won\", totals.won],\n  [\"Lead Rate\", leadRate+\"%\"],\n  [\"Close Rate\", closeRate+\"%\"]\n];\ndocument.getElementById(\"kpiCards\").innerHTML = cards.map(c=>`\n<div class=\"card\">\n  <div class=\"label\">${c[0]}</div>\n  <div class=\"value\">${c[1]}</div>\n</div>`).join(\"\");\n\n/* ===== TABLE ===== */\ndocument.getElementById(\"table\").innerHTML = `\n<tr>\n  <th>Channel</th>\n  <th>Visitors</th>\n  <th>Leads</th>\n  <th>Demo</th>\n  <th>Proposal</th>\n  <th>Won</th>\n</tr>` + report.data.map(r=>`\n<tr>\n  <td>${r[\"Channel\"]}</td>\n  <td>${r[\"Visitors\"]}</td>\n  <td>${r[\"Leads\"]}</td>\n  <td>${r[\"Demo Booked\"]}</td>\n  <td>${r[\"Proposal Sent\"]}</td>\n  <td>${r[\"Won\"]}</td>\n</tr>`).join(\"\");\n\n/* ===== VISITORS CHART ===== */\nnew Chart(document.getElementById('visitorsChart'),{\n  type:'bar',\n  data:{\n    labels: report.data.map(r=>r[\"Channel\"]),\n    datasets:[{\n      label:'Visitors',\n      data: report.data.map(r=>r[\"Visitors\"]),\n      backgroundColor:['#4f46e5','#10b981','#f59e0b']\n    }]\n  },\n  options:{responsive:true, plugins:{legend:{display:false}}}\n});\n\n/* ===== FUNNEL CHART ===== */\nnew Chart(document.getElementById('funnelChart'),{\n  type:'line',\n  data:{\n    labels:[\"Visitors\",\"Leads\",\"Demo\",\"Proposal\",\"Won\"],\n    datasets:[{\n      label:'Total Funnel',\n      data:[\n        totals.visitors,\n        totals.leads,\n        totals.demo,\n        totals.proposal,\n        totals.won\n      ],\n      borderColor:'#4f46e5',\n      backgroundColor:'rgba(79,70,229,0.2)',\n      tension:0.4\n    }]\n  },\n  options:{responsive:true, plugins:{legend:{display:false}}}\n});\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"},"typeVersion":1.2},{"id":"cb3e5738-77bd-48e1-bcb1-6b2c0192bf4d","name":"Get Data From Sheet","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[1936,576],"parameters":{"url":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10mj6hngkPTg1_A6bVNn8QfKujap6j-Lrt_LwAkY2d7Q/gviz/tq?tqx=out:csv&sheet=Sheet1","options":{"response":{"response":{"responseFormat":"file"}}}},"typeVersion":4.4},{"id":"2e4db897-dc00-42e5-9354-0ab19c48b2f0","name":"Upload new HTML Page","type":"@custom-js/n8n-nodes-pdf-toolkit-v2.pdfToolkit","position":[3568,672],"parameters":{"pageName":"Test","resource":"page","htmlContent":"={{ $json.html }}"},"credentials":{"customJsApi":{"id":"d0EHxiyZak4WWRfy","name":"CustomJS account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"44c26dcf-6d1c-432f-9376-6459773e07ab","name":"Get HTML Pages","type":"@custom-js/n8n-nodes-pdf-toolkit-v2.pdfToolkit","position":[2992,576],"parameters":{"resource":"page","operation":"getAll"},"credentials":{"customJsApi":{"id":"d0EHxiyZak4WWRfy","name":"CustomJS account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d2abf284-2362-4c10-9517-73f146a71857","name":"Filter","type":"n8n-nodes-base.filter","position":[3168,576],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"version":3,"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":true,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"46880300-d0eb-44b8-b64b-331207dd7965","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"},"leftValue":"={{ $json.name }}","rightValue":"Test"}]}},"typeVersion":2.3,"alwaysOutputData":true},{"id":"dcdaeac6-81c5-460a-9b25-1587c4233f42","name":"If","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[3328,576],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"version":3,"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":true,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"91e4c5cb-5fb2-4db5-b71b-03c4c8486eb7","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"exists","singleValue":true},"leftValue":"={{ $json.workspaceId }}","rightValue":""}]}},"typeVersion":2.3},{"id":"8bdb57bb-840a-45cd-8436-96450b07b96a","name":"Update existing HTML Page","type":"@custom-js/n8n-nodes-pdf-toolkit-v2.pdfToolkit","position":[3568,496],"parameters":{"pageId":"={{ $json.pageId }}","pageName":"Test","resource":"page","operation":"update","htmlContent":"={{ $('HTML').item.json.html }}"},"credentials":{"customJsApi":{"id":"d0EHxiyZak4WWRfy","name":"CustomJS account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"17c0b30a-f52b-4754-954d-8ba79224a616","name":"Convert HTML to PDF","type":"@custom-js/n8n-nodes-pdf-toolkit-v2.pdfToolkit","position":[4128,560],"parameters":{"html":"=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>KPI Dashbaord</title>\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qrcodejs/1.0.0/qrcode.min.js\"></script>\n<style>\nbody {\n  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n  background: #f6f7fb;\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 24px;\n  color: #111;\n}\n.container {\n  max-width: 400px;\n  margin: auto;\n  background: #fff;\n  padding: 24px;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\nh1 {\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n#qrcode {\n  margin-top: 24px;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n  <h1>KPI Dashboard</h1>\n  <div id=\"qrcode\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\nconst url = \"{{ $json.htmlFileUrl }}\";\n\nnew QRCode(document.getElementById(\"qrcode\"), {\n  text: url,\n  width: 200,\n  height: 200,\n  colorDark: \"#4f46e5\",\n  colorLight: \"#ffffff\",\n  correctLevel: QRCode.CorrectLevel.H\n});\n</script>\n\n</body>\n</html> ","operation":"htmlToPdf","pdfHeightMm":120},"credentials":{"customJsApi":{"id":"d0EHxiyZak4WWRfy","name":"CustomJS account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"edc4e969-fb70-4cb1-b982-23375c67d27b","name":"Extract from File","type":"n8n-nodes-base.extractFromFile","position":[2160,576],"parameters":{"options":{}},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"81b572cd-85e1-4563-a253-eeeadfafd2b1","name":"Aggregate","type":"n8n-nodes-base.aggregate","position":[2352,576],"parameters":{"options":{},"aggregate":"aggregateAllItemData"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"13c815af-b8c2-4f44-b6a1-02aaf31a6e91","name":"Schedule Trigger","type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","position":[1696,704],"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{}]}},"typeVersion":1.3}],"pinData":{},"connections":{"If":{"main":[[{"node":"Update existing HTML Page","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Upload new HTML Page","type":"main","index":0}]]},"HTML":{"main":[[{"node":"Get HTML Pages","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Filter":{"main":[[{"node":"If","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Aggregate":{"main":[[{"node":"HTML","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Get HTML Pages":{"main":[[{"node":"Filter","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Schedule Trigger":{"main":[[{"node":"Get Data From Sheet","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract from File":{"main":[[{"node":"Aggregate","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Get Data From Sheet":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract from File","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upload new HTML Page":{"main":[[{"node":"Convert HTML to PDF","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update existing HTML Page":{"main":[[{"node":"Convert HTML to PDF","type":"main","index":0}]]},"When clicking ‘Execute workflow’":{"main":[[{"node":"Get Data From Sheet","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}